        "language": "IT",
        "source": "ANSA",
        "local_time": "2024-05-12 23:00:30",
        "timezone": "Europe/Rome",
        "scraping_time": "2024-05-12T23.00.30",
        "en_title": "Blinken, from offensive to Anarchy Rafah without eliminating Hamas",
        "en_content": "An offensive to Rafah\nIt would cause \"anarchy\" without eliminating Hamas. He said that\nSecretary of State Antony Blinken in an interview with Nbc,\nstressing that the United States \"have not yet seen a\nplan on what will happen the day after the end of the war\nin Gaza.\"\n\n\n\n\n\nReproduction reserved © Copyright ANSA\n\n\n\n",
        "en_subtitle": "'We haven't seen any plan for after the end of the war'",
